The ethanolic extract of CCF was examined for qualitative screening of various phytochemicals as per standard procedures (
 Sofowora, 1996; 
 Trease and Evans, 2002; 
 Thakur and Shah, 2016). The preliminary tests in the extracts were conducted to confirm the presence of anthocyanins, anthraquinones, alkaloids, carbohydrates, flavonoids, glycosides, phenols, proteins and amino acids, saponins, steroids, and terpenoids.
